## When to use this component

Use this component when there is a requirement for a user to select and submit a local file as part of their task.

## How to use this component

The `<input>` value is set to `type="file"`. A file upload input also takes the attribute `accepts=` which take a comma seperated list of file extensions with the `.` prefix for example: `accept=".xls,.xlsx,.pdf"`.

