### Error messages

Use the [correct errors pattern](/patterns/error-validation) and show the error details above the checkbox options.

{{
    patternlibExample({"path": "components/upload/examples/upload-error/index.njk"})
}}

#### If a file has not been selected
Use “Select a file”.

#### If the file is not valid
Use “Select a file that is either a [list valid formats]”.

For example, “Select a file that is either a PDF, XLS or XLSX”.

#### If the file is too big
Use “Select a file that is less than [whatever the maximum is]”.

For example, “Select a file that is less than 10MB”.

#### If there was a problem and the file could not be uploaded
Use “There was a problem uploading the file. Please try again”.

